entries.name: dct:Agent
entries.description: A resource that acts or has the power to act.

entries.name: dct:AgentClass
entries.description: A group of agents.

entries.name: dct:BibliographicResource
entries.description: A book, article, or other documentary resource.

entries.name: dct:Box
entries.description: The set of regions in space defined by their geographic coordinates according to the DCMI Box Encoding Scheme.

entries.name: dct:FileFormat
entries.description: A digital resource format.

entries.name: dct:Frequency
entries.description: A rate at which something recurs.

entries.name: dct:ISO3166
entries.description: The set of codes listed in ISO 3166-1 for the representation of names of countries.

entries.name: dct:ISO639-2
entries.description: The three-letter alphabetic codes listed in ISO639-2 for the representation of names of languages.

entries.name: dct:ISO639-3
entries.description: The set of three-letter codes listed in ISO 639-3 for the representation of names of languages.

entries.name: dct:Jurisdiction
entries.description: The extent or range of judicial, law enforcement, or other authority.

entries.name: dct:LicenseDocument
entries.description: A legal document giving official permission to do something with a resource.

entries.name: dct:LinguisticSystem
entries.description: A system of signs, symbols, sounds, gestures, or rules used in communication.

entries.name: dct:Location
entries.description: A spatial region or named place.

entries.name: dct:LocationPeriodOrJurisdiction
entries.description: A location, period of time, or jurisdiction.

entries.name: dct:MediaType
entries.description: A file format or physical medium.

entries.name: dct:MediaTypeOrExtent
entries.description: A media type or extent.

entries.name: dct:MethodOfAccrual
entries.description: A method by which resources are added to a collection.

entries.name: dct:MethodOfInstruction
entries.description: A process that is used to engender knowledge, attitudes, and skills.

entries.name: dct:Period
entries.description: The set of time intervals defined by their limits according to the DCMI Period Encoding Scheme.

entries.name: dct:PeriodOfTime
entries.description: An interval of time that is named or defined by its start and end dates.

entries.name: dct:PhysicalMedium
entries.description: A physical material or carrier.

entries.name: dct:PhysicalResource
entries.description: A material thing.

entries.name: dct:Point
entries.description: The set of points in space defined by their geographic coordinates according to the DCMI Point Encoding Scheme.

entries.name: dct:Policy
entries.description: A plan or course of action by an authority, intended to influence and determine decisions, actions, and other matters.

entries.name: dct:ProvenanceStatement
entries.description: Any changes in ownership and custody of a resource since its creation that are significant for its authenticity, integrity, and interpretation.

entries.name: dct:RFC1766
entries.description: The set of tags, constructed according to RFC 1766, for the identification of languages.

entries.name: dct:RFC3066
entries.description: The set of tags constructed according to RFC 3066 for the identification of languages.

entries.name: dct:RFC4646
entries.description: The set of tags constructed according to RFC 4646 for the identification of languages.

entries.name: dct:RFC5646
entries.description: The set of tags constructed according to RFC 5646 for the identification of languages.

entries.name: dct:RightsStatement
entries.description: A statement about the intellectual property rights (IPR) held in or over a resource, a legal document giving official permission to do something with a resource, or a statement about access rights.

entries.name: dct:SizeOrDuration
entries.description: A dimension or extent, or a time taken to play or execute.

entries.name: dct:Standard
entries.description: A reference point against which other things can be evaluated or compared.

entries.name: dct:URI
entries.description: The set of identifiers constructed according to the generic syntax for Uniform Resource Identifiers as specified by the Internet Engineering Task Force.

entries.name: dct:W3CDTF
entries.description: The set of dates and times constructed according to the W3C Date and Time Formats Specification.

entries.name: dct:abstract
entries.description: A summary of the resource.

entries.name: dct:accessRights
entries.description: Information about who access the resource or an indication of its security status.

entries.name: dct:accrualMethod
entries.description: The method by which items are added to a collection.

entries.name: dct:accrualPeriodicity
entries.description: The frequency with which items are added to a collection.

entries.name: dct:accrualPolicy
entries.description: The policy governing the addition of items to a collection.

entries.name: dct:alternative
entries.description: An alternative name for the resource.

entries.name: dct:audience
entries.description: A class of agents for whom the resource is intended or useful.

entries.name: dct:available
entries.description: Date that the resource became or will become available.

entries.name: dct:bibliographicCitation
entries.description: A bibliographic reference for the resource.

entries.name: conformsTo
entries.description: An established standard to which the described resource conforms.

entries.name: dct:contributor
entries.description: An entity responsible for making contributions to the resource.

entries.name: dct:coverage
entries.description: The spatial or temporal topic of the resource, spatial applicability of the resource, or jurisdiction under which the resource is relevant.

entries.name: dct:created
entries.description: Date of creation of the resource.

entries.name: dct:creator
entries.description: An entity responsible for making the resource.

entries.name: date
entries.description: A point or period of time associated with an event in the lifecycle of the resource.

entries.name: dct:dateAccepted
entries.description: Date of acceptance of the resource.

entries.name: dct:dateCopyrighted
entries.description: Date of copyright of the resource.

entries.name: dct:dateSubmitted
entries.description: Date of submission of the resource.

entries.name: dct:description
entries.description: An account of the resource.

entries.name: dct:educationLevel
entries.description: A class of agents, defined in terms of progression through an educational or training context, for which the described resource is intended.

entries.name: dct:extent
entries.description: The size or duration of the resource.

entries.name: dct:format
entries.description: The file format, physical medium, or dimensions of the resource.

entries.name: dct:hasFormat
entries.description: A related resource that is substantially the same as the pre-existing described resource, but in another format.

entries.name: dct:hasPart
entries.description: A related resource that is included either physically or logically in the described resource.

entries.name: version
entries.description: A related resource that is a version, edition, or adaptation of the described resource.

entries.name: id
entries.description: An unambiguous reference to the resource within a given context.

entries.name: dct:instructionalMethod
entries.description: A process, used to engender knowledge, attitudes and skills, that the described resource is designed to support.

entries.name: dct:isFormatOf
entries.description: A pre-existing related resource that is substantially the same as the described resource, but in another format.

entries.name: dct:isPartOf
entries.description: A related resource in which the described resource is physically or logically included.

entries.name: dct:isReferencedBy
entries.description: A related resource that references, cites, or otherwise points to the described resource.

entries.name: dct:isReplacedBy
entries.description: A related resource that supplants, displaces, or supersedes the described resource.

entries.name: dct:isRequiredBy
entries.description: A related resource that requires the described resource to support its function, delivery, or coherence.

entries.name: dct:isVersionOf
entries.description: A related resource of which the described resource is a version, edition, or adaptation.

entries.name: dct:issued
entries.description: Date of formal issuance of the resource.

entries.name: dct:language
entries.description: A language of the resource.

entries.name: dct:license
entries.description: A legal document giving official permission to do something with the resource.

entries.name: dct:mediator
entries.description: An entity that mediates access to the resource.

entries.name: dct:medium
entries.description: The material or physical carrier of the resource.

entries.name: dct:modified
entries.description: Date on which the resource was changed.

entries.name: dct:provenance
entries.description: A statement of any changes in ownership and custody of the resource since its creation that are significant for its authenticity, integrity, and interpretation.

entries.name: dct:publisher
entries.description: An entity responsible for making the resource available.

entries.name: dct:references
entries.description: A related resource that is referenced, cited, or otherwise pointed to by the described resource.

entries.name: dct:relation
entries.description: A related resource.

entries.name: dct:replaces
entries.description: A related resource that is supplanted, displaced, or superseded by the described resource.

entries.name: dct:requires
entries.description: A related resource that is required by the described resource to support its function, delivery, or coherence.

entries.name: dct:rights
entries.description: Information about rights held in and over the resource.

entries.name: dct:rightsHolder
entries.description: A person or organization owning or managing rights over the resource.

entries.name: dct:source
entries.description: A related resource from which the described resource is derived.

entries.name: dct:spatial
entries.description: Spatial characteristics of the resource.

entries.name: dct:subject
entries.description: A topic of the resource.

entries.name: dct:tableOfContents
entries.description: A list of subunits of the resource.

entries.name: dct:temporal
entries.description: Temporal characteristics of the resource.

entries.name: dct:title
entries.description: A name given to the resource.

entries.name: dct:type
entries.description: The nature or genre of the resource.

entries.name: dct:valid
entries.description: Date (often a range) of validity of a resource.
